snippet.textDisplay:
Man, I remember seeing Vivzie ‘s first animations wayyy back in 2015, and now, she’s improved so much to even have her own team to make Hazbin Hotel, Helluva Boss, etc. When she 1st showed an animation WIP in 2017 of Hazbin, I was eager to see it. I love the pilot already. The animation looks soooo professional and should be an actual show airing. This shows how far Viv has come in her animation career.
I don’t know, she might not see this, but if she does, then I’m telling her how amazing her works are for me and she’s been one of my inspirations for animation in general. :)
snippet.textOriginal:
Man, I remember seeing Vivzie ‘s first animations wayyy back in 2015, and now, she’s improved so much to even have her own team to make Hazbin Hotel, Helluva Boss, etc. When she 1st showed an animation WIP in 2017 of Hazbin, I was eager to see it. I love the pilot already. The animation looks soooo professional and should be an actual show airing. This shows how far Viv has come in her animation career. 
I don’t know, she might not see this, but if she does, then I’m telling her how amazing her works are for me and she’s been one of my inspirations for animation in general. :)
